{"tid":1435604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解藍絲會知道好多示威者都唔知既嘢","createTime":"2019-08-09T05:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:25:42.000Z","uid":288632,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"502b36845083d25335b4975da432d5f538fa462b","tid":1435604,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:52:33.000Z","msg":"Whatapp傳緊～<br />\n<br />\n今個星期日盡量留守家中🙏🏻<br />\n警方己確認左<br />\n*11/8港岛東區會有大型示威*<br />\n除左北角之前講過的路程外,<br />\n另外<br />\n- 柴灣, <br />\n- 筲箕灣,<br />\n- 太古城,<br />\n- 鰂魚涌<br />\n- 大型住宅及商場<br />\n一樣有示威<br />\n確認 包圍<br />\n- 北角海關總部,<br />\n- ICAC總部,<br />\n- 北角警署,<br />\n- 北角碼頭,再經過<br />\n- 電器道行去大型嘅<br />\n-住宅<br />\n- 城市花園<br />\n- 和富花園同埋呢個<br />\n- AIA 嘅保險中及<br />\n- 附近酒店。<br />\n 轉載:<br />\n剛剛警隊稱，香港警察部收到最高指示（強調是最高），<br />\n從收到通告即時開始，不再驅散，<br />\n只會拘捕撿控，<br />\n全部從暴動入罪<br />\n（最高可判十年以上），不考慮人數多少，<br />\n通知身邊親朋，<br />\n唔好去睇熱閙，<br />\n講明有殺錯冇放過。"},{"pid":"5ac89382ecca561304d676ccb3c6bb1d2b848dbe","tid":1435604,"uid":140335,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"因為全部所謂嘅消息都係佢哋自己作出黎"},{"pid":"972ab0f13091d4a315f86fbd7e72d5e4860664e8","tid":1435604,"uid":12086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:57:22.000Z","msg":"（強調是最高）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb3984e1e0d195d4a658a2e69d9622e03f3ac16","tid":1435604,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"可以點回應～佢好乞人憎～公司高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e77b1678764e1a8e8b372df4218faaeef4b7716","tid":1435604,"uid":249960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abb3984e1e0d195d4a658a2e69d9622e03f3ac16","tid":1435604,"uid":288632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"可以點回應～佢好乞人憎～公司高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:25:42.000Z","msg":"問